140
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,280
Are you Zhang Lurang?

141
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,960
Lurang.

142
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,720
-Wang Yang.
-Here.

143
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,480
-Han Zheng.
-Here.

144
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,360
-Li Maosheng.
-Here.

145
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,680
-Zhang Renli.
-Your books.

146
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,720
They're in order.

147
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,360
What took you so long?

148
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,680
I was late and stopped

149
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,080
