150
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,080
What?

151
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:35,200
So then, what are you going to do?

152
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,160
Are you nervous?

153
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,240
No.

154
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,960
I'm just concerned about you.

155
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,360
I've heard

156
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:44,760
that tardy students' names get recorded.

157
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,000
