-My name wasn't recorded.

158
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,320
It wasn't?

159
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,880
I'm glad to hear that.

160
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,680
Or Zhang Lurang would appear twice.

161
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,240
Don't you think

162
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,720
