163
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,400
Am I?

164
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,760
Not at all.

165
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,400
And you're not only interested,

166
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,720
but also

167
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,080
a little bit guilty.

168
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,360
Am I?

169
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,840
Actually, I didn't do anything

170
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,360
that would hurt you too much.

171
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,760
Where are you going?

172
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,000
The broadcast studio.

173
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:20,960
The broadcast studio?

174
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:26,320
The more I think, the weirder I feel.

175
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,680
Why did Zhang Lurang pretend
to be in our class?

176
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,320
Maybe he misremembered his class number.

177
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,360
I'm guessing he did that deliberately.

178
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:39,120
