from their class when someone was late.

179
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,320
Su Zaizai,

180
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,920
only you haven't paid for the uniform yet.

181
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,480
Okay, I'll pay for it now.

182
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,520
Where is my wallet?

183
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,040
I picked up a wallet.

184
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,680
Is there any ID in it?

185
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,040
I haven't opened it.

186
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,520
Look inside.

187
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,080
You might find the owner's ID in there.

188
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,680
I told you to check.

189
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,000
You just wouldn't listen.

190
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,880
I remember

191
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,520
I put it in my pocket this morning.

192
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,680
Calm down, Zaizai.

193
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:28,040
How about I pay for it first? Then you...

194
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,680
You can do a lost-and-found broadcast.

195
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,840
Maybe a student picked it up.

196
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,680
Is your student ID card in your wallet?

197
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,080
Yes.

198
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,360
That makes things simple.

199
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,120
The ID has your photo and name on it.

200
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,240
Whoever finds it will know it is yours.

201
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,360
But...

202
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,440
But I didn't put my name

203
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,720
on my student ID card.

204
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,200
Then whose name is it?

205
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,520
It's...

206
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,960
It's...

207
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,000
<i>Attention.</i>

208
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,400
<i>This is a lost-and-found broadcast.</i>

209
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,000
<i>High school student, Liu Yifei.</i>

210
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,600
<i>High school student, Liu Yifei,</i>

211
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,520
<i>please come to the broadcast studio</i>

212
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,440
<i>to pick up your lost wallet.</i>

213
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,200
Is there a Liu Yifei here?

214
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,880
Then I could be Daniel Wu!

215
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:20,120
I'm Joey Wong. Nice to meet you.

216
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,000
Nice to meet you.

217
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,640
I'll stop looking for my wallet now.

218
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,040
Look, what a good day today!

219
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,280
I'm going out for some fresh air.

220
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:31,080
What's the hurry?

221
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,120
Wait.

222
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,880
Su Zaizai,

223
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,440
you're that Liu Yifei, aren't you?

224
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,200
THE FIRST HIGH SCHOOL, LIU YIFEI

225
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,960
Yes, it's me.

226
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,440
High school student, Liu Yifei?

227
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,360
Check if anything is missing.

228
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,120
"Zhang Lurang. Gu Ran."

229
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,200
