230
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:07,320
Were they the ones who found this wallet?

231
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,800
Two boys brought it here.

232
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:10,840
They just left.

233
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,840
Zhang Lurang?

234
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,640
Isn't he the guy we met this morning?

235
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,320
We can still catch up. Hurry.

236
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,640
Faster, Zaizai.

237
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,560
There they are.

238
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:29,480
Zaizai, hurry up.

239
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,840
