240
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,160
Zhang Lurang! Gu Ran!

241
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,320
Hey!

242
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:43,960
Hey!

243
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:48,960
What? I didn't get a good look.

244
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,200
Gu Ran?

245
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,600
It's him. Is his name Gu Ran?

246
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,320
Do you know him?

247
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,360
I've seen him at the corner store.

248
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,960
What?

249
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,440
Regarding military training,

250
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,920
that is all I have to say.

251
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,360
Now, I'll talk about disciplines.

252
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:32,000
Today is the first day of school.

253
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,560
But some students were still late.

254
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,400
The Office of Academic Affairs told me

255
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,200
