256
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,760
will have to stand guard

257
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,240
at the military training base.

258
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,320
Nine students were late this morning.

259
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:47,360
Two are from our class, the honors class.

260
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,040
Someone was not only late,

261
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,960
but also misremembered his class.

262
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,760
What is it?

263
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,960
Do you wish to be in Class 9?

264
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,320
Let me read their names.

265
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,680
From our class,

266
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,360
Zhang Lurang

267
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,920
and Gu Ran.

268
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:09,680
Su Zaizai and Jiang Jia.

269
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,960
Behave when you're punished tomorrow.

270
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,200
Try to be the most energetic students.

271
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,800
<i>Tomorrow morning at 8 a.m.,</i>

272
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,160
